text: Saúl Cofiño (born 12 July 1978) is a Spanish gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Spain Category:Gymnasts at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Barcelona
